Prompt 2.2.3: Create Filter Components
Objective: Build filtering and sorting UI components.
Instructions for AI Agent:

Create filtering components:

1. src/components/filters/CategoryList.astro:
   - Accept props: categories (Category[]), activeCategory (string | undefined)
   - Display vertical list of categories
   - Each category:
     - Name
     - Video count (in lighter text)
     - Active state styling (different background)
   - Include "All Categories" option at top
   - Styling:
     - Each item: padding, hover state
     - Active: primary color background, white text
     - Hover: light background

2. src/components/filters/TagFilter.astro:
   - Accept props: tags (Tag[]), activeTags (string[])
   - Display horizontal scrollable list of tag chips
   - Each tag:
     - Pill/chip shape
     - Clickable
     - Toggle active state (different color when selected)
   - Styling:
     - Chips with border
     - Active: filled with primary color
     - Inactive: border only
     - Hover effect

3. src/components/filters/SortOptions.astro:
   - Accept props: currentSort (SortOption)
   - Display dropdown or button group:
     - Newest
     - Oldest
     - Most Viewed
     - Highest Rated
   - Show currently selected option
   - Styling:
     - Dropdown button with icon
     - Light background
     - Border

4. Create a filter bar component that combines these:
   - src/components/filters/FilterBar.astro
   - Horizontal layout on desktop
   - Stacks vertically on mobile
   - Contains: TagFilter and SortOptions
   - Sticky below header when scrolling

DELIVERABLE: Complete filter components with intuitive UI.